#summary BaseClass Members

== Properties ==

object[.Pair]( _( Null | "property" )_ )
description: manuplate data on jsObject or jsArray, Null mean is auto unique variables 
type: any primitive value or json data structure object

object.Collection
description: raw data structure
type: Scripting.Dictionary

object.Count
description: contains new auto unique variable, is have a only number
type: Number

object.QuotedVars
description: variable warp quotes

object.Kind

object.jsString

object.Clean
description: remove all items in data structure
return: none

object.Remove(_Item_)
description: remove only selected item in data structure
return: none

object.Flush
description: convert and send JSON data to output
type: none
